      <h3>Curated Phonegap Plugins</h1>
      <p>Application Craft developers can include plugins from the IDE. Non AC developers just modify the config.xml. We are adding more plugins all the time.</p>

      <ul class="clearfix">
        <li>
          <h4>Push Notifications</h4>
          <p>We have integrated with the Xtify platform.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4>Scandit</h4>
          <p>Scandit offers commercial grade barcode reading from your smartphone.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4>Google ZXing</h4>
          <p>An excellent, free barcode reader for smartphones.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4>SQLite Database</h4>
          <p>Add relational database capabilities to your App.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4>Mail To</h4>
          <p>Access your devices email capabilties from your App.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4>Child Browser</h4>
          <p>Have a browser window within your App so your user does not end up in the device browser. Much nicer!</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

